headline: How Investors May Respond To Zimmer Biomet (ZBH) Pairing a Q4 Dividend With OneStep Mobility Analytics
summary: Zimmer Biomet Holdings recently announced that its Board approved a fourth-quarter 2025 cash dividend of US$0.24 per share, payable on or about January 30, 2026 to shareholders of record as of December 30, 2025. The company also entered an exclusive collaboration with OneStep to embed smartphone-based gait and mobility analytics into its mymobility Care Management Platform, deepening its push into data-driven, connected orthopedic care. headline: Will Direct Distribution in Southern Europe Boost ISRG's Margins?
summary: ISRG plans a 2026 shift to direct distribution in Italy, Spain, and Portugal, aiming to lift margins by capturing distributor economics with execution risk.
